      <description>Healthcare and medical MCP servers are connecting AI agents to clinical data, medical research, drug databases, and imaging systems via the Model Context Protocol. We reviewed 30&#43; servers across 6 subcategories. FHIR/EHR Integration: wso2/fhir-mcp-server (98 stars, Python, Apache-2.0 — expose any FHIR server as MCP with full CRUD, SMART-on-FHIR auth, stdio/SSE/HTTP transport), jmandel/health-record-mcp (75 stars, TypeScript, MIT — SMART on FHIR EHR access with grep/SQL/JavaScript query tools), the-momentum/fhir-mcp-server (68 stars, Python, MIT — 11 tools for FHIR resources with Pinecone vector search and LOINC integration), rkirkendall/medplum-mcp (14 stars, TypeScript, MIT — 33 tools for Medplum FHIR CRUD), langcare/langcare-mcp-fhir (15 stars, Go — enterprise-grade EHR proxy for Epic/Cerner/GCP with 40&#43; clinical skills library, TLS 1.3, PHI scrubbing), AWS HealthLake MCP (part of awslabs/mcp 8.5K stars — 11 FHIR tools with automatic datastore discovery, read-only mode, 96% test coverage). Medical Research: JackKuo666/PubMed-MCP-Server (104 stars, Python, MIT — 5 tools for PubMed search/metadata/PDF download/deep analysis, most starred research MCP server), cyanheads/clinicaltrialsgov-mcp-server (58 stars, TypeScript, Apache-2.0 — 7 tools for ClinicalTrials.gov with trend analysis/patient matching/study comparison, 92% test coverage), JackKuo666/ClinicalTrials-MCP-Server (15 stars, Python, MIT — 7 tools with CSV export), pascalwhoop/medical-mcps (14 stars, Python, MIT — 100&#43; tools across 14 biomedical APIs including PubMed/OpenFDA/KEGG/UniProt/GWAS/ChEMBL). Multi-Source Healthcare Hubs: Cicatriiz/healthcare-mcp-public (101 stars, JavaScript, MIT — 9 tools for FDA drugs/PubMed/clinical trials/ICD-10/DICOM/medical calculator, most starred healthcare MCP server), JamesANZ/medical-mcp (75 stars, TypeScript, MIT — 15 tools for FDA/WHO/PubMed/Google Scholar/RxNorm/AAP, no API keys needed, fully local). Drug &amp; Pharmacology: openpharma-org/drugbank-mcp-server (2 stars, JavaScript, MIT — 17,000&#43; drug records with interactions/pathways/structure search via SQLite), openpharma-org/nlm-codes-mcp (0 stars, TypeScript, MIT — ICD-10/ICD-11/HCPCS/NPI/HPO/LOINC/RxTerms via NLM Clinical Tables API). Medical Imaging: ChristianHinge/dicom-mcp (86 stars, Python, MIT — 11 tools for DICOM/PACS query/move/PDF extraction, most starred imaging MCP server), fluxinc/dicom-mcp-server (3 stars, Python, LGPL-2.1 — DICOM connectivity testing). Healthcare Standards &amp; Compliance: innovaccer/Healthcare-MCP (28 stars, Python, MIT — HMCP specification extending MCP for HIPAA compliance with OAuth 2.0/SMART-on-FHIR/audit logging), Cicatriiz/pophive-mcp-server (17 stars, JavaScript — Yale PopHIVE public health surveillance data with 11 datasets). Rating: 4.0/5.</description>
