    <item>
      <title>Social Media &amp; Marketing MCP Servers — Twitter/X, Bluesky, Instagram, LinkedIn, Meta Ads, Google Ads, SEO, and More</title>
      <link>https://chatforest.com/reviews/social-media-marketing-mcp-servers/</link>
      <guid>https://chatforest.com/reviews/social-media-marketing-mcp-servers/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 09:55:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <description>Social media and marketing MCP servers are turning AI agents into social media managers, ad campaign operators, and SEO analysts — letting them post content, analyze engagement, manage ads, and track rankings via the Model Context Protocol. We reviewed 40&#43; servers across 6 subcategories. Twitter/X Posting &amp; Analytics: EnesCinr/twitter-mcp (375 stars, TypeScript, MIT, 2 tools — post_tweet/search_tweets, most popular Twitter MCP server), vidhupv/x-mcp (61 stars, Python, MIT — draft management, thread composition, direct publishing), taazkareem/twitter-mcp-server (19 stars, JavaScript, MIT — 11 tools across reading/interaction/timeline/user management), adhikasp/mcp-twikit (Python — unofficial API access without developer account), crazyrabbitLTC/mcp-twitter-server (TypeScript — professional workflow automation), 0xGval/twitter-X-mcp-server (lightweight Claude search integration). Bluesky &amp; AT Protocol: cameronrye/atproto-mcp (6 stars, TypeScript, MIT — 57 tools, most comprehensive AT Protocol integration with social ops/data retrieval/content management/list moderation/real-time streaming/batch operations/analytics/OAuth), semioz/bluesky-mcp (7 stars, JavaScript — 11 tools for posts/likes/reposts/profiles/timeline, featured in official MCP server repo). Instagram: jlbadano/ig-mcp (88 stars, Python — 8 tools for Instagram Business accounts via Graph API with publishing/analytics/DMs), Bob-lance/instagram-engagement-mcp (engagement tracking/lead generation), anand-kamble/mcp-instagram (profile/timeline/stories/engagement), BilalTariq01/instagram-analytics-mcp (Graph API analytics/insights). LinkedIn: adhikasp/mcp-linkedin (Python — feeds and job API), felipfr/linkedin-mcpserver (profile search/jobs/messaging), eliasbiondo/linkedin-mcp-server (people/company/job search with structured JSON), Rayyan9477/linkedin_mcp (job search/resume generation/cover letters). Multi-Platform Social: vanman2024/ayrshare-mcp (1 star, Python — 75&#43; tools across 15 categories, 13 platforms including Facebook/Instagram/Twitter/LinkedIn/TikTok/YouTube/Pinterest/Reddit/Snapchat/Telegram/Threads/Bluesky/Google Business), Seym0n/tiktok-mcp (137 stars, JavaScript, MIT — 3 tools for subtitle extraction/post details/search via TikNeuron), anaisbetts/mcp-youtube (503 stars, JavaScript, MIT — yt-dlp subtitle extraction for video summarization). Advertising &amp; Paid Media: pipeboard-co/meta-ads-mcp (628 stars, Python, BSL 1.1 — 26 tools for Meta/Facebook/Instagram ads with campaign management/creative operations/performance analytics/targeting/budget scheduling), google-marketing-solutions/google_ads_mcp (129 stars, Python, Apache-2.0 — campaign/ad group/metrics retrieval from Google Ads API, experimental), amekala/ads-mcp (19 stars, Shell, proprietary — 100&#43; tools across Google/Meta/LinkedIn/TikTok ads), gomarble-ai/facebook-ads-mcp-server (Facebook Ads programmatic access), attainmentlabs/meta-ads-mcp (campaign creation/management from Claude). SEO &amp; Content Marketing: cnych/seo-mcp (224 stars, Python, MIT — 4 tools for backlinks/keyword generation/traffic/keyword difficulty based on Ahrefs data), ahrefs/ahrefs-mcp-server (94 stars, TypeScript — official but archived, superseded by remote MCP at mcp.ahrefs.com), metehan777/semrush-mcp (12 stars, TypeScript, MIT — 7 tools for domain overview/keyword research/organic search/backlinks/competitor research), mrkooblu/semrush-mcp (Semrush API data access). Email Marketing: Iterable/mcp-server (3 stars, TypeScript, MIT — official, 26-105 tools depending on permissions for campaigns/templates/user profiles/event tracking/message sending), AgentX-ai/mailchimp-mcp (TypeScript, MIT — read-only Mailchimp Marketing API access), LokiMCPUniverse/mailchimp-mcp-server (Python — comprehensive Mailchimp API with rate limiting). Social Media Management: LokiMCPUniverse/hootsuite-mcp-server (Python — Hootsuite API integration), tn819/buffer-mcp (Buffer scheduling), HubSpot official MCP at developers.hubspot.com/mcp (CRM &#43; marketing integration). The ecosystem is massive but fragmented — Twitter/X alone has 8&#43; community MCP servers with overlapping features. Meta Ads leads advertising at 628 stars with professional-grade campaign management. YouTube&#39;s most popular server (503 stars) only extracts subtitles. The AT Protocol/Bluesky space is early but atproto-mcp&#39;s 57 tools show ambition. SEO tooling is split between free Ahrefs scrapers and official-but-limited integrations. Multi-platform posting through Ayrshare covers 13 platforms but has minimal traction. Email marketing is well-served by Iterable&#39;s official 105-tool server. Overall: strong breadth across platforms, weak depth on most individual platforms.</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Desktop Automation &amp; Browser Control MCP Servers — Playwright, Selenium, Windows-MCP, macOS Automator, and More</title>
      <link>https://chatforest.com/reviews/desktop-automation-rpa-mcp-servers/</link>
      <guid>https://chatforest.com/reviews/desktop-automation-rpa-mcp-servers/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 09:45:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <description>Desktop automation and browser control MCP servers give AI agents eyes and hands — the ability to see screens, click buttons, type text, and control applications through the Model Context Protocol. We reviewed 30&#43; servers across browser automation (microsoft/playwright-mcp at 28,900 stars — official, accessibility-tree-driven web interaction without vision models; executeautomation/mcp-playwright at 5,300 stars with 143 device presets and test code generation; angiejones/mcp-selenium at 374 stars for Selenium WebDriver with multi-browser support; browserbase/mcp-server-browserbase at 3,200 stars for cloud browser sessions; BrowserMCP/mcp at 6,100 stars — Chrome extension automating existing logged-in browser), Windows desktop (CursorTouch/Windows-MCP at 4,700 stars with Snapshot/DOM modes and 0.2-0.9s latency; mario-andreschak/mcp-windows-desktop-automation at 102 stars wrapping AutoIt functions), macOS desktop (steipete/macos-automator-mcp at 711 stars with 200&#43; AppleScript/JXA recipes and accessibility queries; joshrutkowski/applescript-mcp at 368 stars with Calendar/Finder/Mail/Messages/Notes/Shortcuts integration; antbotlab/mac-use-mcp at 1 star with 18 zero-dependency tools), cross-platform desktop (AB498/computer-control-mcp at 120 stars with PyAutoGUI/RapidOCR/ONNXRuntime; manushi4/Screenhand at 17 stars with 88 tools across vision/input/browser/anti-detection), and enterprise RPA (UiPath official MCP platform integration with coded/command server modes). Microsoft Playwright MCP dominates browser automation with accessibility-tree snapshots that outperform screenshot-based approaches; Windows-MCP leads desktop control with the most stars and fastest response times; macOS has the richest scripting ecosystem through AppleScript/JXA.</description>
    </item>
    
